- From d6g: backup-before-edit.sh, audit-bash-commands.sh, log-all-operations.sh, validate-changes.sh, handle-notifications.sh, prompt-analysis.sh, cleanup-on-stop.sh, subagent-cleanup.sh, session-cleanup.sh, pre-compact-backup.sh, session-init.sh, prompt-security-scan.sh, security-session-init.sh
